item.title: Use Azure DevOps Demo Generator to create a new Project in Azure DevOps
item.author: Jev
item.description: This is the 3rd post in the category Azure DevOps Fundamentals of the blog post series on working with Azure DevOps In this post the I will introduce you to the Azure DevOps Demo Generator tool by using it ot to create a new Project in Azure DevOps. Since it much more fun to do research and play with technology in collaboration with others, Wesley Camargo will be covering some of the topics on he’s blog , while other topics are covered by my here.
